


                        Welcome to OpenClovis SDK
                        =========================

1. Content
----------

   This distribution contains OpenClovis SDK, a development and run-time
   environment for the OpenClovis Application Service Platform (ASP).
  
   OpenClovis ASP is middleware that provides High Availability (HA),
   System Management, and other common carrier grade services, primarily
   addressing the infrastructure needs of complex communication devices.
   

2. How to Install
-----------------

   For more information on software pre-requisites and the complete procedure
   to install OpenClovis SDK, refer to the installation guide accompanying this
   package at doc/pdf/openclovis_installguide_3.0.pdf or 
   doc/html/installguide/index.html.
